This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with improving machine translation systems. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses an active learning-style data solicitation algorithm. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with improving the performance of AI systems. It could also be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with improving the accuracy of translation systems. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as it uses a data solicitation algorithm to improve the performance of the translation system.
